ko‘rinishidan foydaliga o‘xshaydi va 

00:00:17.240 --> 00:00:19.280
shunga e’tibor berishingiz mumkinki, 
qidiruv bo‘yicha ma’lumotlar anchagina

00:00:19.280 --> 00:00:22.770
demak, bu boshqa dasturchilar 
orasida ham keng tarqalgan savol.

00:00:22.770 --> 00:00:24.470
Keling, bu natija bilan tanishamiz. 

00:00:24.470 --> 00:00:27.620
Shunday qilib, "Android" da 
ro‘yxat ko‘rinishida elementni bosish jarayonini 

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:29.890
