00:00:34.030 --> 00:00:36.490
Shuning uchun, siz buni mustaqil 
o‘qishga biroz vaqt sarflashingiz mumkin.

00:00:36.490 --> 00:00:39.790
Ammo bu yerda to‘g‘ridan-to‘g‘ri 
