00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:22.440
Men bu yerda
elementlarni bosganda tinglash 

00:01:22.440 --> 00:01:23.270
usulini aniq topmoqchiman.

00:01:23.270 --> 00:01:25.870
Shunday qilib, u bu yerda birinchisi.

00:01:25.870 --> 00:01:29.010
Ushbu usulning tavsifida 
aytilishicha, ushbu qabul qiluvchi 

00:01:29.010 --> 00:01:32.240
